name: BEACHY_VIEW
description:
Just a typical summer's afternoon in Australia. 
With the hot dry day's just frying and scorching everything in its path including our bodies, we loan for some type of counter measure,, around dinner time or just after The giant hot bastard better known as Mr Sun is clocking out for the day.. As its setting its laying goldn rays on to goldn white sandy cliff's. All with pleasing sounds of the white washing fizzling from in coming waves crashing down then running up to the shore line..
